## Prioritized Implementation Roadmap

### 🚨 Phase 0 — Critical Fixes (Must be done before anything else works)

> These are blockers. Nothing else will function correctly until these are fixed.

| Priority | Fix | File(s) | Impact |
|----------|-----|---------|--------|
| P0-1 | **Fix Django env-var names** — rename `POSTGRES_USER/DB/PASSWORD` to `DB_USER/DB_NAME/DB_PASSWORD` in `.env` **or** fix `settings.py` to read from `POSTGRES_*` vars. | `config/settings.py`, `.env` | Django connects to Neon PostgreSQL instead of SQLite |
| P0-2 | **Fix .env path** — move `.env` to workspace root `d:\VigilX-BE\.env` **or** correct `load_dotenv()` paths in `settings.py` and `utils/config.py`. | `config/settings.py`, `ai-engine/utils/config.py` | Both servers load credentials correctly |
| P0-3 | **Fix Django ORM model** — add real database fields to `FIR`, `Victim`, `Accused` models (crime_type, status, location, latitude, longitude, gender, etc.) removing `@property` stubs. Set `managed = True` and run migrations. | `apps/cases/models.py` | Seeds, tests, and CRUD all work |
| P0-4 | **Wire AI Engine REST endpoints** — add `AI_ENGINE_REST_*_PATH` env variables for `case_search`, `accused_records`, `victim_records`, `crime_records`, `case_summary`, `investigation_status`. | `.env`, `ai-engine/utils/config.py` | `/ai/ask` successfully fetches real data from Django |
| P0-5 | **Add token blacklisting** — install `rest_framework_simplejwt.token_blacklist` to `INSTALLED_APPS` and call `token.blacklist()` in `LogoutView`. | `config/settings.py`, `apps/authentication/views.py` | Logout properly invalidates tokens |

